<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>입찰 등록</title>
</head>
<body>
  <div id="all">
    <div id="header">
      <div id="top">
        <%- include('noLoginMenu') %>
        <a href="/home">
          <img src="/views/image/logo.png" id="logo">
        </a>
      </div>
      <%- include('menu') %>
    </div>
    <div id="main">
        <h2>문의 답변 하기</h2>
        <form method="post" enctype="multipart/form-data">
          <table>
            <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%= post_id %>">
            <tr id="t">
                <td id="tagt">문의 답변</td>
                <td><textarea name="ask_content" id="ask_content" required></textarea></td>
            </tr>
            <tr id="f">
                <td id="tagf">파일</td>
                <td><input type="file" name="file" id="file"/></td>
            </tr>
          </table>
          <button type="submit" id="submit">문의 답변 하기</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div id="bottom">
      <hr>
      <br>
      <p>안산대학교 IT응용보안과 2B04 전자입찰시스템</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
